<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>إن كان لام "فعل<span class="c1">". . . . . . . . . . . .... . . . . . . . . . .<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
